  version:decimal:7.0
    event:sephia.version
  author-readme:@"Sephia Five is a cryptographically secure webmail client, with PGP support. It is built with your privacy in mind, and has the following features.

* PGP cryptography
* Phishing protection
* Easy to use
* Blistering fast compared to GMail

Sephia Five is Free Software, Open Source, and Gratis for individuals - And also features a full API, if you wish to extend it."





